{"tid":433621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3萬7千名Chrome用戶上當，裝了假冒的Adblock Plus","createTime":"2017-10-12T13:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T17:48:02.000Z","uid":66943,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8e92ec32a52be637e5a2cd73fbf5b6a92fdf88c3","tid":433621,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:30:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/117324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F117324&d=3af2D%2Flz%2F1Ki%2Br%2FNG%2FkyisPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ac84b30e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/117324</a><br />\n<br />\n此一假冒的Adblock Plus於今年9月22日上架，宣稱是由Adblock Plus所提供，至本周一（10/9）已有超過3.7萬名Chrome用戶安裝，事件爆發後，Google已將其下架。<br />\n<br />\n[img]<br />\n<a href=\"https://d3jcp1umdd59vg.cloudfront.net/sites/default/files/styles/picture_size_large/public/field/image/adblock_1.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd3jcp1umdd59vg.cloudfront.net%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fpicture_size_large%2Fpublic%2Ffield%2Fimage%2Fadblock_1.jpg&d=3af2D%2Flz%2F1Ki%2Br%2FNG%2FkyisPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=7365b3f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://d3jcp1umdd59vg.cloudfront.net/sites/default/files/styles/picture_size_large/public/field/image/adblock_1.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n一名獨立資信安全研究人員SwiftOnSecurity昨天（10/9）透過Twitter踢爆，一個假冒為Adblock Plus的Chrome擴充程式繞過了Google的審核機制，堂而皇之地登上Chrome Web Store，至少有3.7萬名Chrome用戶受害。<br />\n<br />\n此一假冒的Adblock Plus於今年9月22日上架，宣稱是由Adblock Plus所提供，至本周一（10/9）已有超過3.7萬名Chrome用戶安裝，而正牌的Adblock <a href=\"http://Plus則是來自Adblockplus.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FPlus%E5%89%87%E6%98%AF%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AAAdblockplus.org&d=3af2D%2Flz%2F1Ki%2Br%2FNG%2FkyisPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=8ef1d8df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Plus則是來自Adblockplus.org</a>，用戶人數已突破1000萬，除了商標非常類似之外，所提供的功能也相當，都是宣稱能夠封鎖所造訪網站的廣告。<br />\n<br />\n然而，安裝到假Adblock Plus的用戶卻發現，當他執行Chrome瀏覽器時，該擴充程式即自行開啟大量的分頁。<br />\n<br />\n這與日前爆出Chrome瀏覽器多家外掛程式開發商的帳號外竊事件不同，這名騙子開發人員只是偽造了Adblock Plus的外觀、功能描述、商標與關鍵字，以誤導使用者。<br />\n<br />\nSwiftOnSecurity則批抨Chrome Web Store的審核程序不夠嚴謹，Google並未公開回應此事，但已將偽造的Adblock Plus擴充程式下架。"},{"pid":"3f849a0914c4d2cd29917af0e0cf00af96eb4fcb","tid":433621,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a1eb4d3e7b24f6af4da2449ee46f64d99b581f","tid":433621,"uid":5159,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:39:07.000Z","msg":"先上架後審批"},{"pid":"a8f9a973e7844384c821fbd0392dffce57d211b6","tid":433621,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d97c44d077c64a4120dcc4ff2eddda62ef18096","tid":433621,"uid":8410,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:43:20.000Z","msg":"Google d 野唔會check 下先放上store , 叫user 點會放心用"},{"pid":"e64d1112b9f0107d5517d4bce9be01ede67b5337","tid":433621,"uid":89199,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T13:58:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81039da75f33dd4f25ab401ed6fd5e835ce3fdac","tid":433621,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:07:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你叫人點放心用android呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngoogle play store 審查機制都係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055df9c3e2e23a7f7581169a233f74bc4fc9ffdb","tid":433621,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:20:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你叫人點放心用android呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngoogle play store 審查機制都係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma